entries.femaleVariant: Stop the damn car!
No! Stop! Stop the killing!
It's not their fault! Shoot the girl and our deal is dead!
entries.maleVariant: It's not their fault! Shoot the guy and our deal is dead!

entries.femaleVariant: Come with us. You'll find out all you need to know on the way.
Noted. But you don't have a vote here.
Hah! That's it. Got no fuckin' idea what this is about, but if you don't go with them I'm never talking to you again.
Finally! Somethin' that isn't a complete snorefest. Could binge-watch this all day if I had some popcorn…
Well, this one time Rachel is right – we can't stay here.
They're here to kill you!
We take her with us.
Ah, no thanks. Just be on my way, now.
entries.maleVariant: No thanks. Just be on my way, now.

entries.femaleVariant: Ugh, wastin' time here!
Please? I need you. Really.
Answer's no.
Why do you need me? Why so badly?
Now can we go?
Want me to come... to come with you?
entries.maleVariant: You wa-- you want me to come with you?

entries.femaleVariant: Heh, I need you.
Nobody and I mean nobody, will harm a hair on your head. I'm just uh, heh... borrowing you.
What the hell is this?
V.
Josh Stephenson. But you probably knew that already…
Your... associate – what was his name?
It's OK. You don't need to tell me. My name is Joshua Stephenson.
Aaaand your... associate – what was his name?
Bill Jablonsky. Ring a bell?
Sadly, yes.
"Teach us to number our days, that we may gain a heart of wisdom!"
Already ID'd him. Bill Jablonsky.
Wait a sec, you're V? Eh, I heard o' you!
Well I want to give her a job.
entries.maleVariant: Well I want to give him a job.

entries.femaleVariant: Agh! Christ on a stick…
Gotta object, strongly.
Fuck! Brake, I said! Brake!
Stay close, I'm going to blow the motherfucker to bits myself!
This is it, let's go!
First, gonna tell me what the hell's going on.
entries.maleVariant: First you're gonna tell me what the hell is going on.

entries.femaleVariant: The fuck are you doing? Stop!
NCPD! Stay where you are! And get that goddamn semi outta here!
Right, let's just all shoot holes in each other.
For crying out loud, fuck! We can't leave her here! Media vultures'll be here any minute!
entries.maleVariant: For crying out loud, fuck! We can't leave him here! Media vultures'll be here any minute!

entries.femaleVariant: Gregor? Busted an attempted hit on my guy…
Vasquez! Shoot!
What?!
You're outta your fuckin' mind!
Hey, another word from you and I'm callin' the studio. Don't make me ruin your career.
Hhmm... What's your name?
We can't take her, out of the question. She's way too big a threat.
entries.maleVariant: We can't take him, out of the question. He's way too big a threat.

entries.femaleVariant: Screw this, I'm out.
Aahh... such a shame.
It's OK – go. Nobody's going to stop you.
Gonna tell me what it is you want from me?
Can't say the same about you.
All right. I'll go with you.
I'm not goin' anywhere.
Ugh, move it. We're running late.
Yeah. One cazh.
Loo-- I can explain, just... don't go! I... I need you.
You're insane if you think I'm getting in that car.
Haha, I just, ah... I, um... I really need you, please…
Ugh, ditch the bitch. We gotta go.
entries.maleVariant: Ugh, ditch the dick. We gotta go.

entries.femaleVariant: No. She's coming with us. She has to.
entries.maleVariant: No. He's coming with us. He has to.

entries.femaleVariant: Aughh... Such a shame...
Lieutenant Vasquez, NCPD! Stop right there!
You're protecting a murderer!
Wait!
Drop it, or I shoot!
Want me to come... with you?
I'm not going anywhere.
What the hell you want from me?
Screw this, I'm out.
Why me?
Not about to go anywhere with you.
Got no idea what's going on here.
You're insane.
No thanks, I'm outta here.
V.
What's this about, tell me.
Bill Jablonsky.
[Get in] So be it, I'll go.
NCPD! Stop right there!
You fucking idiot!
[Get out]
Bill Jablonsky. No priors, but run a deep sweep just to be sure.
This… this… what a fuckin' mess…
Told you drop it, dickhead…
Shoulda listened, shoulda fuckin' listened…
We're clear to go. Boys from the precinct'll mop up here.
I'm gonna do it... I'm gonna fucking kill him!
Olga? We've got a situation...
Somebody just tried to drop our star.
That psycho's out hiring professionals! It was only matter of time.
'Cause he's a fucking nutcase, that's why!
What a cunt!
Thanks, I owe you. No patrol car and stay off the frequencies, too. Can't have this comin' back.
Out. Go. Now.
